headline.0: U.S. Culpability in the Failure of Israeli-Palestinian Peace Talks

short_description.0: The Obama administration would have to challenge the Israeli government's hard line toward the Palestinians in order for the peace process to be successful. Unfortunately, the White House apparently had no interest in doing so.
